{"tid":420653,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【嫁個好老外】梁詠琪有西班牙老公 官恩娜嫁中法混血牙醫","createTime":"2017-10-01T14:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T11:43:30.000Z","uid":35964,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ee0a63f41343a86681c3729af5b7101ced1c1d","tid":420653,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:57:32.000Z","msg":"中德混血兒貝安琪今年2月就同外籍男友Simon未婚生咗個好可愛嘅囝囝Sebastian，佢仲話準備喺明年同男友結婚，其實好多圈中靚女都喜歡嫁個好老外，過住好幸福嘅生活呢！<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506687668_df95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170929%2Flarge%2F1506687668_df95.jpg&h=cfe66b0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁詠琪同西班牙籍老公Sergio喺11年結婚，兩人嘅囡囡Sofia都已經兩歲喇，今年為Sofia開生日會選擇低調舉行，只係得至襯同好友出席，佈置好多都係DIY，連蛋糕都係朋友整。早前GiGi仲透露過，想喺年底追多個。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506691282_bd04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170929%2Flarge%2F1506691282_bd04.jpg&h=ec2033d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周汶錡同法籍老公Julien，大仔Jacques都係兩歲，至於細仔Avner就差唔多半歲。為咗紀錄兩個仔嘅成長片段，周汶錡喺ig開咗個page不時update下佢哋嘅新相，用童真去征服fans。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506691286_20f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170929%2Flarge%2F1506691286_20f3.jpg&h=ef5593b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官恩娜就喺前年2月同中法混血牙醫男友Domingo結婚，為咗尊重圈外男友決定，結婚都係低調處理，不過Domingo都好識做，有着中式馬褂影結婚相。同年10月，兩人嘅囝囝B&eacute;B&eacute; G出世，老公仲親手剪臍帶。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506691290_0a7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170929%2Flarge%2F1506691290_0a7e.jpg&h=2a6556d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車婉婉喺愚人節宣佈榮升媽咪，為中澳混血老公Jonathon生咗囝囝 Justus。雖然婉婉係高齡產婦，但佢堅持要自然分娩，體驗十級痛。生產當日痛足十幾個鐘，老公全程陪住。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506691291_4bd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170929%2Flarge%2F1506691291_4bd7.jpg&h=f0c1ced5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李蕙敏喺2013年喺倫敦同拍拖3年嘅英籍男友Serge Micallef結婚，而黃偉文更充當「代父」，到英國送呢個囡囡出嫁㖭！除咗黃偉文，李蕙敏仲請咗關寶慧做伴娘。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506697875_48ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170929%2Flarge%2F1506697875_48ab.jpg&h=361a4b5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97c52137f137fe350bc6da9cbe3cd75e4e1e4329","tid":420653,"uid":39253,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"乜撚野老外,鬼佬就鬼佬啦"},{"pid":"a7a0eabe0533c81aad397a007736f25600f0d96c","tid":420653,"uid":50162,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:03:47.000Z","msg":"老外萬歲！去含洋腸先，掰～"},{"pid":"655a61fdd98a555fbc270bc7b4784ee920b3f760","tid":420653,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:16:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老外萬歲！去含洋腸先，掰～</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1f2b32e2dc21572ed52249827e95a215c5ebd2","tid":420653,"uid":77569,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:23:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"890dc2044db1bab00cc088b3a1d93db0f4d1c0c6","tid":420653,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚野老外,鬼佬就鬼佬啦</blockquote><br />\n冇撚錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92dec32a93b79e623d060d1a2dba21a5120d2d3","tid":420653,"uid":121349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:25:35.000Z","msg":"周汶琦老公都幾型，其他果d真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0ff6a3224fdbce551f91e8a3a616e7d6fdeb56","tid":420653,"uid":67840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:28:33.000Z","msg":"咁多條洋腸無個靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221bf1e2e72fb07d960de2f5bee93b169b3736b8","tid":420653,"uid":9062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多條洋腸無個靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有💰又有洋腸含，就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}